<i>noun</i>: 샌님 [샌ː님] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>샌님 [샌ː님]</dt><br>
<dd>1. nerd; geek</dd><br>
<dd>(옛날에) 평민이 선비를 이르던 말.</dd><br>
<dd>(archaic) A term used by a commoner to address a scholar.</dd><br>
<dd>2. narrow-minded person; petty person</dd><br>
<dd>(놀리는 말로) 얌전하고 소심하며 융통성이 없는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>(teasing) A person who is docile, timid, and inflexible.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>